    "# CCTV Unpaid Customer & Long-Stay Without Order Detector\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook contains a prototype for a system that detects unpaid customers and individuals who stay for a long time without placing an order in a food-serving establishment. It uses YOLOv8 for object detection and tracking, and provides a simple GUI to display the results."
